1
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,530
He sent you,

2
00:00:25,430 --> 00:00:26,630
Ying Wujiu.

3
00:00:27,130 --> 00:00:29,300
He made you personally send me to his bed.

4
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:31,100
And you actually accepted this decree.

5
00:00:31,100 --> 00:00:34,230
Helan Ci wants to use this extremely twisted way

6
00:00:34,530 --> 00:00:36,860
to completely crush Ying Wujiu's dignity

7
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,530
and warn me at the same time.

8
00:00:39,130 --> 00:00:40,000
Thunder or rain,

9
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,230
are all the Emperor's grace.

10
00:00:41,230 --> 00:00:42,400
This dancing dress,

11
00:00:42,660 --> 00:00:45,300
the Emperor ordered you to wear it to serve him tonight.

12
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:47,030
My hands are injured.

13
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:48,560
I can't untie my clothes.

14
00:00:49,230 --> 00:00:52,100
I'll have to trouble the Chief to undress me personally.

15
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:53,900
Ying Wujiu, aren't you a eunuch?

16
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:57,160
You personally put this torn dress on me.

17
00:00:57,660 --> 00:00:58,360
Qu Jingzhi.

18
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:01,000
Will you only be satisfied when you drive me to death?

19
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:01,700
Ying Wujiu,

20
00:01:02,630 --> 00:01:04,629
you finally can't pretend anymore.

21
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:11,700
That night, Helan Ci fell asleep due to a headache,

22
00:01:11,700 --> 00:01:13,960
and didn't actually call me to serve him.

23
00:01:15,330 --> 00:01:16,430
Jingzhi.

24
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,930
Look at the birds in this pavilion.

25
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,960
I spent a fortune to find each of them.

26
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:23,490
But none of them

27
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,060
is like you, a canary that can heal,

28
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,600
who pleases me.

29
00:01:27,730 --> 00:01:29,530
Your Majesty is the true dragon.

30
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,560
I'm just a lowly life in the mud.

31
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,930
If I say you are a rare treasure, you are.

32
00:01:34,259 --> 00:01:35,000
Jingzhi.

33
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:36,360
I will issue a decree tomorrow

34
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,360
to make you a Noble Lady

35
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,900
and grant you the main hall of Yanxi Palace.

36
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:39,759
From now on,

37
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:41,229
you don't need to return to the Yeting Bureau.

38
00:01:41,229 --> 00:01:42,400
Your life and your body,

39
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:45,229
will be locked by my side for eternity.

40
00:01:45,229 --> 00:01:46,090
He's watching.

41
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:47,289
I can't be exposed,

42
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:51,130
otherwise Helan Ci will immediately have him shot to death.

43
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,630
Helan Ci,

44
00:01:53,860 --> 00:01:55,560
you don't just want to kill me,

45
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:57,560
you also want to break her spine

46
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,690
and turn her into a plaything in a cage.

47
00:01:59,729 --> 00:02:02,360
Since this cannibalistic imperial power wants to lock her up,

48
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,260
then I

49
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:06,000
will personally smash this palace cage

50
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:07,260
and take you away.

51
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:13,290
Congratulations.

52
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:15,160
You'll be a Noble Lady tomorrow.

53
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:17,460
The Prime Minister ordered me to deliver the final death order.

54
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:19,060
The Prime Minister wants to assassinate the Emperor

55
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:20,460
and frame the Eastern Depot.

56
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,800
The castrated dog blocked the Prime Minister's way,

57
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,000
so he naturally must die.

58
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,230
If you obey obediently,

59
00:02:24,230 --> 00:02:26,000
the Prime Minister will leave your corpse intact.

60
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
If you dare to have second thoughts,

61
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:31,260
you should know what those three years in the water dungeon felt like.

62
00:02:31,260 --> 00:02:32,000
You...

63
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,360
Yu Henian,

64
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,860
you shouldn't have,

65
00:02:36,100 --> 00:02:38,600
you absolutely shouldn't have threatened me with his life.

66
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,600
Yu Henian's secret letter of treason and private army deployment.

67
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,400
With this,

68
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,260
I can expose Yu Henian's plot,

69
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,430
break free from his control,

70
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,100
and never be controlled again.

71
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,960
I must go find Wujiu immediately.

72
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:55,100
Wearing Helan Ci's golden lock,

73
00:02:55,100 --> 00:02:56,630
where do you want to escape?

74
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,460
Ying Wujiu!

75
00:02:59,260 --> 00:03:00,960
I got Yu Henian's secret letter of treason

76
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,800
and the private army deployment.

77
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,530
Take me away.

78
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,460
Are you okay, Jingzhi?

79
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,400
Hold me tight.

80
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:39,930
Even if the King of Hell comes for you today,

81
00:03:39,930 --> 00:03:41,530
I will get you out.

82
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:47,230
Ying Wujiu, wake up.

83
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,730
You liar.

84
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:52,190
Didn't you say you could retreat unscathed?

85
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:09,530
You.

86
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,060
You are still here.

87
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,360
You are not crippled.

88
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:16,160
Besides the deadly poison, the Yu family's arrows

89
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,000
were also coated with

90
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:20,000
a strong aphrodisiac meant for martial arts masters.

91
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,600
Jingzhi, don't touch me.

92
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:24,060
Don't you know I'm a normal man?

93
00:04:24,130 --> 00:04:24,730
If you light the fire now,

94
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:26,060
I will burn you to ashes.

95
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,600
Jingzhi.

96
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,230
My little empress.

97
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:39,760
I finally hold you in my arms.

98
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,890
What did you call me?

99
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,030
Ying Wujiu.

100
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,430
You remember the past life too,

101
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,230
don't you?

102
00:04:45,330 --> 00:04:46,460
You were reborn too.

103
00:04:46,659 --> 00:04:47,320
Ying Wujiu.

104
00:04:47,659 --> 00:04:48,500
Listen well.

105
00:04:48,730 --> 00:04:50,260
In the past life, you died for me.

106
00:04:50,260 --> 00:04:51,700
In this life, you fell into hell for me.

107
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:52,530
From now on,

108
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,760
don't even think about pushing me away.

109
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,230
Today,

110
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:56,460
I will give myself to you completely.

111
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:58,060
My Jingzhi.

112
00:04:58,460 --> 00:05:00,430
Even if tomorrow brings a bottomless abyss,

113
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,490
I will never let go.

114
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,890
What's going on?

115
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:16,030
The secret guards who went to Yanxi Palace

116
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:18,500
and the assassins who ambushed Ying Wujiu outside Shenwu Gate,

117
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,560
why hasn't a single one returned to report?
